":1190312,"uid":230198,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"cbea8d82493c26ada9a5115110c7a7a66bdee2c1","tid":1190312,"uid":200000,"like":9,"dislike":29,"score":-20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"佢啲片真心幾高質<br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得拍太多放題同自助餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T12:59:14.000Z","msg":"自助餐唔知有咩野食<br />\n人頭$500 600起跳, 成本唔細<br />\nyoutube 可以一次睇哂裝修, 食物, 迫唔迫, 景觀等等, 都值得睇<br />\n反而上次講愛文生, 我就唔太有興趣<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 上次食 Bao俾人屈100蚊一杯水, 好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/35DOSdJOL08\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F35DOSdJOL08&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ujbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=ec46bc99\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/35DOSdJOL08</a>"},{"pid":"1545b4a36ae873d41ec9a7eae7bc878e24d8152e","tid":1190312,"uid":247139,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"呢排先做香港youtuber仲有十五萬訂閱<br />\n己經吸引到至少一半成日睇YouTube嘅香港人<br />\n只能講香港YouTube唔值得有咁高質嘅youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2be402f1a31f6b1f5b042d3121dd50b8e4e026a","tid":1190312,"uid":13257,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"1545b4a36ae873d41ec9a7eae7bc878e24d8152e","tid":1190312,"uid":247139,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"呢排先做香港youtuber仲有十五萬訂閱<br />\n己經吸引到至少一半成日睇YouTube嘅香港人<br />\n只能講香港YouTube唔值得有咁高質嘅youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:45:29.000Z","msg":"全靠果對on9兩公婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec3eefd2258c5a0a2af9070c8b3c36487441f8b","tid":1190312,"uid":76063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:50:28.000Z","msg":"評過百里香"},{"pid":"817142f03652a8b24815af098640ea108dd4eb28","tid":1190312,"uid":68457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T14:57:58.000Z","msg":"所以我唔會睇youtube餐廳評論"},{"pid":"f8a87c6c35da43a1d2c60526a49f4160ee04f18c","tid":1190312,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:03:02.000Z","msg":"睇王剛好過啦<br />\n<br />\n大師傅唔係得個批評<br />\n<br />\n做比你睇<br />\n<br />\n份人又nice"},{"pid":"289247d1fb6d83662e47fc549ea66c7e6992e36d","tid":1190312,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":37,"score":-35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:04:34.000Z","msg":"睇死佢咪又係得個講<br />\n<br />\n點整都未識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> d評價好行貨<br />\n<br />\n王剛屌打"},{"pid":"06fa03b633aab9fb09eaae75e026c5b49e889ede","tid":1190312,"uid":140094,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:06:42.000Z","msg":"佢老婆d 護膚品review都好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f36d696b19d13c069bd5eaa6d09ef80b1e5843","tid":1190312,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":34,"score":-32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T15:10:01.000Z","msg":"香港果d扮野就識 未見過佢地煮<br />\n<br />\n人地王剛真心分享<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EhyQom5jiTE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEhyQom5jiTE&d=SmQqe2lJFulj5u2s5Cv8ujbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=58b44d70\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EhyQom5jiTE</a>"},{"pid":"c342575c5a165e91a627cd985e3a88b4db1bdd8f","tid":1190312,"uid":251696,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201